<exercise checkit-seed="0004" checkit-slug="AppDiffTanLine" checkit-title="Equations of tangent lines">
    <statement>
        <p>
        Let <m>f(x) = -2 \, x^{4} + 2 \, x^{3} + 3 \, x + 2</m>. Find an equation of the line tangent to the graph at the point <m>(-3, -223)</m>.
        </p>

    </statement>
    <answer>
        The equation of the tangent line is <m>y = 273 \, x + 596</m>.
    </answer>
</exercise>
